PLACEHOLDER_FAQ_TITLE: Frequently Asked Questions About Our Blockchain Analytics App
ACCORDION_ANSWER_1: Our app provides in-depth analysis of new blockchain data as it gets added to the decentralized ledger. It parses transaction details, smart contract executions, and other on-chain activity to give you insights into emerging trends and patterns.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_2: We connect directly to blockchain nodes to ingest raw data as soon as new blocks are mined. This data is then processed through our analytics engine which extracts relevant information and metrics based on customizable filters you set.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_3: Currently we support analysis for Ethereum, Bitcoin, and several major Ethereum layer-2 solutions like Polygon and Arbitrum. More chains will be added based on user demand.
ACCORDION_ANSWER_4: Sign up for a free account to access our app and analytics dashboard. The onboarding process will guide you through connecting blockchain nodes and customizing your analysis parameters.
FAQ_SUBTITLE_PLACEHOLDER_TEXT: Get answers to common questions about our blockchain data analysis platform
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_1: Blockchain analytics refers to the process of analyzing data from blockchain networks to gain insights into transactions, addresses, smart contracts, and overall network activity. Our platform provides powerful tools to extract, process, and visualize this data.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_2: We currently support analysis of data from Bitcoin, Ethereum, and several other major blockchain networks. Our roadmap includes expanding coverage to more networks based on user demand.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_3: How can I use the analytics data?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_3: The analysed blockchain data can be used for compliance monitoring, fraud detection, supply chain tracking, financial analysis and more. Our flexible APIs and data exports allow you to integrate the insights into your own applications and workflows.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_QUESTION_TEXT_4: Is the data updated in real-time?
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_4: Yes, our platform ingests new blockchain data as it gets added to the networks and updates the analysis automatically. You'll always have access to the latest blockchain intelligence.
FAQ_PLACEHOLDER_ANSWER_TEXT_5: Sign up for a free trial to explore our blockchain analytics platform. Our documentation provides guides to querying data, and our support team is available to assist with any questions.
